{"tid":2131568,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"禁堂食其實係對黃色經濟圈打左支強心針","createTime":"2020-07-30T03:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T04:27:36.000Z","uid":35870,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8697bdde85f57970067ef172a10c1462b825d6","tid":2131568,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:05:14.000Z","msg":"經濟差，其實就是自由市場底下淘汰一班無生產力嘅公司/人的天然機制<br />\n<br />\n通常最有競爭力的公司都會趁住呢段時間擴張/投資落R&amp;D<br />\n<br />\n今次禁堂食，首當其衝，自然是一堆target customer同社會脫節嘅餐廳，好似一大堆藍絲酒樓咁樣，平時無搞開外賣無搞開電子化，班target customer又個個老到連電話都唔識用，所以先一大堆咁執粒，根本就係跟唔上時代步伐，不進則退<br />\n<br />\n相反，黃金經濟圈，若果大家肯繼續堅持只叫黃店外賣，挨過今次疫情之後，其他藍店收晒皮，自然得返一大堆黃店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840b64efa576584768b5c9814fff0807de86318f","tid":2131568,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:06:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8df0d94d79b856068c8598f33789eab6d076bdfb","tid":2131568,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca93483e8a324dd9465728d4cea58e4e7f205782","tid":2131568,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"莫講話外賣app，海鮮酒家藍店早市做點心、晚市做蒸魚、魚翅湯嗰啲貴嘢，點外賣？<br />\n稻香、富臨呢啲廢老藍店仲爆病毒群組，抵撚死啦！<br />\n<br />\n首要要幫嘅黃店，應該係小店，尤其日本菜、文青cafe、素自助餐，嗰啲好難做外賣，但住附近嘅，10分鐘左右返到公司、屋企嘅，盡量先救呢啲先！仲要自備餐具，環保兼減輕黃店即棄餐具嘅經營成本！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bd75a7c2143458374c088977e10ddc200e9c95","tid":2131568,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"屌出完po無耐就話放寛2人堂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21950a8db990583498b54690642ee738ee6935af","tid":2131568,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84bd75a7c2143458374c088977e10ddc200e9c95","tid":2131568,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"屌出完po無耐就話放寛2人堂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02c961eb8a01f0546961fea7839498ec9f5fe3a","tid":2131568,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:32:00.000Z","msg":"玩尻死藍店就啱<br />\n今日放寛聽日再收緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd685a72ed3aebc9e3f110b91f9c9cce28d87c7","tid":2131568,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84bd75a7c2143458374c088977e10ddc200e9c95","tid":2131568,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"屌出完po無耐就話放寛2人堂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"都唔緊要 個道理都啱<br />\n<br />\n原來可能用黎打壓黃色經濟圈<br />\n點知政府低估咗科技同香港人嘅進步<br />\n用apps叫黃店又得 排隊黃店外賣又得<br />\n<br />\n我都明白黃店都難捱 但有香港人盡救<br />\n而大財團嘅藍店成本因鋪多開支一定大<br />\n長期無生意 藍店一定會骨牌效應咁執"},{"pid":"fcf54510734476794eb68abb94827b4f8dde53fb","tid":2131568,"uid":170944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"無知&hellip;&hellip;限商令丫禁堂食丫之類，死先既一定係黃店，一黎黃絲帶得把口既姐，撐得幾多，唔出名既黃店食緊風啦，二黎藍店大多係中資或集團式經營，點會早死過黃店？"}]}